* {{flag|France}} – 外交部长[[让-马克·埃罗|让-马克·埃罗]]向遇难者家属表示慰问并表示：“法国在这悲惨的情况下向遇难者家属表示慰问。法国会在恐怖主义面前站在巴基斯坦当局这边。”<ref><cite class="citation web">[https://en.dailypakistan.com.pk/pakistan/france-condemns-attack-on-quetta-police-training-centre/ "France condemns attack on Quetta police training centre"] {{Wayback|url=https://en.dailypakistan.com.pk/pakistan/france-condemns-attack-on-quetta-police-training-centre/ |date=20161028215101 }}. </cite></ref><ref><cite class="citation web">[http://www.brecorder.com/pakistan/general-news/324873-france-condemns-terrorist-attack-in-quetta.html "France condemns attack on Quetta"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.brecorder.com/pakistan/general-news/324873-france-condemns-terrorist-attack-in-quetta.html |date=20161027132516 }}. brecorder.com. 25 October 2016<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref> 

* {{flag|Japan}} – [[日本外務省|外務省]]{{Link-ja|外務發言人|外務報道官|發言人}}川村泰久谴责此次袭击：“日本强烈谴责这种把目标定为无辜的人的恐怖主义行为”，并向遇难者家属表示慰问：“日本向遇难者家属表示慰问，也祈福受害者早日回归日常生活。”<ref><cite class="citation web">[https://www.thenews.com.pk/latest/141273-Japan-condemn-terrorist-attacks-QuettafromNewsdog=1 "Japan condemn the terrorist attacks in Quetta"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.thenews.com.pk/latest/141273-Japan-condemn-terrorist-attacks-QuettafromNewsdog=1 |date=20161028152409 }}. </cite></ref>他还表示日本将会与巴基斯坦政府合作：“日本打算与国际社会一起支持巴基斯坦政府打击恐怖主义的行为。”<ref><cite class="citation web">[http://www.app.com.pk/japan-condemns-quetta-terrorist-attack/ "Japan condemns Quetta terrorist attack"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.app.com.pk/japan-condemns-quetta-terrorist-attack/ |date=20161028153059 }}. </cite></ref> 

* {{flag|Germany}} – 外交部长[[弗兰克-瓦尔特·施泰因迈尔|弗兰克-瓦尔特·施泰因迈尔]]指责这起袭击：“我们谴责奎达警察学校发生的恐怖袭击，其中有超过60人死亡...我们向巴基斯坦的所有人民表示最深切的哀悼。”<ref><cite class="citation web">[https://sputniknews.com/world/201610251046695561-pakistan-germany-quetta/ "Attack on Police Academy in Pakistan"] {{Wayback|url=https://sputniknews.com/world/201610251046695561-pakistan-germany-quetta/ |date=20161028215031 }}. </cite></ref>   

